        "heading": "The Three Levers",
        "content": "```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    API REQUEST                          │\n│                                                         │\n│  1. MODEL RIGHT-SIZING          \"Use the right tool\"    │\n│     Opus → Sonnet → Haiku       Saves 60-80%           │\n│                                                         │\n│  2. PROMPT CACHING              \"Don't repeat yourself\" │\n│     Cache stable prefixes        Saves 85-90% on reads  │\n│                                                         │\n│  3. BATCH API                   \"Wait for the discount\" │\n│     Async 24hr processing        Saves 50% flat         │\n│                                                         │\n│  COMBINED                       All three stacked       │\n│     Haiku + cached + batched     Saves 90-95%           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---"
