        "heading": "Stacking All Three: The 90%+ Strategy",
        "content": "### Architecture\n```\n                    ┌──────────────┐\n   Incoming Tasks → │  CLASSIFIER  │ (Haiku — pennies)\n                    │  Route by    │\n                    │  complexity  │\n                    └──────┬───────┘\n                           │\n              ┌────────────┼────────────┐\n              ▼            ▼            ▼\n         ┌────────┐  ┌─────────┐  ┌────────┐\n         │ HAIKU  │  │ SONNET  │  │  OPUS  │\n         │ 60-70% │  │ 25-35%  │  │  5-10% │\n         │ of vol │  │ of vol  │  │ of vol │\n         └───┬────┘  └────┬────┘  └───┬────┘\n             │            │           │\n             ▼            ▼           ▼\n    ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐\n    │         PROMPT CACHING                 │\n    │  Cache system prompts + tool defs      │\n    │  90% off on repeated prefix tokens     │\n    └────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n                     │\n              ┌──────┴──────┐\n              ▼             ▼\n        ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n        │ REAL-TIME │  │  BATCH   │\n        │ (stream)  │  │ (async)  │\n        │ Standard  │  │ 50% off  │\n        └──────────┘  └──────────┘\n```\n\n### Combined Cost Example\n```\nWorkload: 10,000 requests/day, avg 2K input + 500 output tokens\n\nALL OPUS, NO OPTIMIZATION:\n  20M × $5 + 5M × $25 = $100 + $125 = $225/day\n\nFULLY OPTIMIZED:\n  Step 1 — Route (60% Haiku, 35% Sonnet, 5% Opus):\n    Haiku:  12M × $1 + 3M × $5   = $12 + $15   = $27\n    Sonnet: 7M × $3 + 1.75M × $15 = $21 + $26.25 = $47.25\n    Opus:   1M × $5 + 0.25M × $25 = $5 + $6.25  = $11.25\n    Subtotal: $85.50 (62% savings from routing alone)\n\n  Step 2 — Cache (80% hit rate on 1.5K of 2K input = stable prefix):\n    Cache reads save ~70% of remaining input cost\n    Subtotal: ~$45 (80% savings from baseline)\n\n  Step 3 — Batch non-urgent (50% of volume):\n    50% off on half the requests\n    Subtotal: ~$33 (85% savings from baseline)\n\n  RESULT: $225/day → ~$33/day = 85% reduction\n```\n\n---"
