        "heading": "Overview",
        "content": "This module covers the complete landscape of modern deposit infrastructure — the $2.3T wholesale funding market that ModernFi is digitizing. These five pods connect to form a single thesis: **banks have modern frontends but 1990s backends for balance sheet management, and the post-SVB world demands real-time, API-first deposit infrastructure**. Understanding how these pieces fit together — reciprocal deposits, wholesale funding, credit union networks, analytics, and core banking integrations — gives you the complete picture of what ModernFi is building and why it matters."
